title: NFC North Breakdown + Dobbins Doubt, Jet Logs - Fantasy Football Podcast for 7/5
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, the divisional breakdowns begin! Andy, Mike, and Jason discuss offseason moves for the NFC North, while projecting for the 2022 fantasy football season! What can we expect from the Packers without Davante Adams? Darnell Mooney or Adam Thielen? Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for July 5th, 2022
